<h2>Maintain Zookeeper</h2>
<h3>Export ZK to S3</h3>
<div>
Exports will be saved with the configuration bucket to a folder specific to the stack.
An export will be saved with a date and timestamp.
The export will also be saved as <code>latest_snapshot.out</code>.
</div>
<form method="POST" action="/ops/zk/snapshot">
  <input type="submit" value="Snapshot ZK and Save to S3"/>
</form>
<h3>Restore ZK from S3</h3>
<div>
Exports are saved with the configuration bucket to a folder specific to the stack.
The file will be restored from the file <code>latest_snapshot.out</code>.
</div>
<form method="POST" action="/ops/zk/restore">
  <input type="submit" value="Restore ZK from S3" class="button_red"
  onclick="return confirm('This will erase the current ZooKeeper state and restore from the snapshot. Are you sure you want to proceed?')"/>
</form>
</div>
